name: Scooby and the GAN, Part 1: Wastelands
description:
Mystery Incorporated didn’t survive the apocalypse, and Scooby is no longer his same old self. Is that Shaggy chilling out on far left? Or crouching in that fur coat on the far right? As for the other characters, it looks like Scooby’s got a whole new gang to hang with.

Note: No input image was used for this VQGAN+CLIP art.

2944x2240 pixel PNG
